{
  "texts": [
    "The results showed that the transformer-based models performed better than the NNbased solutions, registering a 95% F1-score for QARiB.",
    "Fouad et al. [86] conducted another experiment for detecting fake news.",
    "The research used two datasets.",
    "The first contains news and tweets collected manually by the researchers and annotated to rumor or non-rumor, while the second dataset was from [87].",
    "The two datasets were merged and used to create a third one."
  ]
}